## Proposed threshold

> **LLM-ON precision ≥ <N>%** over the held-out set, where a case PASSes iff its
> **deterministic** layer and its **standard** layer both hold (metric.md).

<N>% is the product's own `precision_threshold_pct` (SPEC §<x>), now applied to a
**real, executed** measurement rather than a hardcoded stub constant.

